metadata.name: DAY01
metadata.description:
HELLO WORLD.

You all know what is going on in Ukraine right now. Since 5am 24th of February 2022 Russia kills Ukrainian nation for nothing. 

This audio-visual artwork is an interpretation of how people in our country woke up on that very first day of the war.

This collection will feature archival artworks from the war crime scene.

Proceeds from the project support Ukranian Emergency Art Fund, who support artists and cultural workers during the war. and our own ongoing activism and art. 

PLEASE KEEP DONATING AND STANDING WITH UKRAINE.
